July 27, 2017 9:44 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Caravelle Investment Fund II, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Caravelle Investment Fund II, LLC specializes in investment in four asset categories: leveraged loans; high yield bonds; mezzanine securities; and private equity. The fund is a market-value collateralized bond obligation fund.


295 Madison Avenue6th FloorNew York, NY 10017United StatesFounded in 2000



